{"tid":1659066,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《爐石》美國大學生比賽舉牌「撐香港」後，暴雪今禁賽半年","createTime":"2019-10-16T18:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T01:54:41.000Z","uid":28765,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a261161c8e258d93c79033d5781c8a11406b5730","tid":1659066,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/puku-clone-version/199cd432f5c65f273001908f87991db1c17eff65.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fpuku-clone-version%2F199cd432f5c65f273001908f87991db1c17eff65.png&h=989665d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n還記得前陣子於北美舉辦的《爐石戰記》官方校園賽事，華盛頓美利堅大學（American University）選手在比賽直播期間對鏡頭舉牌「光復香港」而遭導播緊急切掉畫面，如今 AU 大學選手透過推特發布，表示已收到暴雪官方通知，戰隊遭半年禁賽懲處。<br />\n<br />\n上週，《爐石戰記》官方校園賽事，由伍斯特理工學院（Worcester Polytechnic Institute）對決華府美利堅大學，就在 AU 大學選手在敗陣前，學生們刻意舉出「Free Hong Kong, boycott Blizzard」字牌，而畫面急忙被導播切掉，連投降畫面都沒播出來，在網路社群引起話題。<br />\n<br />\n在事情發生後，北美資深電競記者 Rod Breslau 在推特表示，暴雪與 TeSPA 當時決定不處罰 AU 大學的舉牌動作，並且已安排好他們的下一場比賽。不過，AU 大學的三位選手表示將會退出官方校際賽，且不認同暴雪對自己的不處份決定（因為聰哥被禁賽，他們卻沒有），他們在接受 VICE 訪問時也證實這一點。<br />\n<br />\n如今事隔一週，暴雪正式寄出對 AU 大學的懲處信件通知，根據 Casey Chambers 選手推特，他們因違反官方比賽規章（PDF）中的 7.1.B「運動家精神與專業素養」，祭出 6 個月的禁賽懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n對此，Casey Chambers 在推文中表示他們早就知道會有後果，對懲罰結果並不意外。根據 VICE 訪問，Chambers 一行人舉牌的用意就是想表達對聰哥禁賽事件的關心，並希望暴雪有所反應，對於預期內的懲罰，他們表示欣然接受。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/puku-clone-version/34c99a2470f244eef2f4de12331bb8ffe8ba7ce8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fpuku-clone-version%2F34c99a2470f244eef2f4de12331bb8ffe8ba7ce8.jpg&h=81458f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/40763/au-hearthstone-team-received-a-six-month-ban-from-competition-by-blizzard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F40763%2Fau-hearthstone-team-received-a-six-month-ban-from-competition-by-blizzard&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgJa4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=80394bc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/40763/au-hearthstone-team-received-a-six-month-ban-from-competition-by-blizzard</a><br />\n<br />\n係咁轉軑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee3845f488e96b053ab80eb7f5ca03f27e45958","tid":1659066,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:35:58.000Z","msg":"ok 新一輪風暴嚟喇"},{"pid":"ef4ed5041fcc8f2acb2d7284ab01e24c8f495abe","tid":1659066,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:40:39.000Z","msg":"本來都已經冇咩人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757dbeb14ca25ca6d7c4baf1a85fc6658aa4b40a","tid":1659066,"uid":2949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:41:21.000Z","msg":"又撥火"},{"pid":"77f011c5bd9cf57bfed30d0ab00b00e7d7d5730a","tid":1659066,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:42:10.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0cfb9e5a05ac313e80866586f28b05afa43c6b","tid":1659066,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:43:06.000Z","msg":"隊死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42e29e92385afaa22fe09c2aa8ad5fe4aa74572","tid":1659066,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:44:17.000Z","msg":"有冇Twitter推？"},{"pid":"f52c4f16a1fc520d3cee8a07233e1b3598629661","tid":1659066,"uid":236003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:44:20.000Z","msg":"Blizzard係咪曲線想美國人keep住留意支共同香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f119f89dac7d3aa2b1613582f70aec668359b99e","tid":1659066,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislik